Description: read-only MCP server for NetBox infrastructure data
 A read-only Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that enables LLMs to
 interact with NetBox infrastructure data. Built with FastMCP, it exposes
 NetBox's DCIM, IPAM, circuits, virtualization, tenancy, VPN, and wireless
 objects as read-only tools for LLM-driven queries.
 .
 Only GET operations are exposed; no create/update/delete tools are
 provided. Connection details are supplied via NETBOX_URL and
 NETBOX_TOKEN environment variables.
